The Abdominal Volume Index (AVI) is suggested as a new obesity index that can be used to estimate abdominal fat rather than total visceral body fat [49]. It has been reported that body fat percentage, body fat mass, and BMI are highly correlated with AVI [50].\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
